data.text:
@dracula70136224 Hi, at this moment we don't have any information about what might happen after 12/21 regarding the Eurobonus extension unfortunately. I recommend that you keep yourself updated at https://t.co/S8T8R6SHZj for the latest Eurobonus information.

Best regards,
Anton.

@katyraines Hi, I am sorry to hear that your flight was cancelled. Please contact us by live-chat https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj with your booking reference and we can help you with the ticket number.

Best regards,
Anton.

@diririradiririr Hello, please contact our live-chat support and we can help you take a look at this over there. We are not able to look into specific cases over Twitter unfortunately https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards,
Anton.

@hildeo Hej, jag känner inte till några problem med vår hemsida för tillfället men om du upplever problem på hemsidan så kan du ringa oss eller live-chatta med oss för hjälp. Öppettider är kl 07-19 på vardagar, 09-17 lördag och 09-18 söndag.

Med vänlig hälsning,
Anton.

@ValeriaGissi Hello! I would recommend that you contact our phone support for assistance with the rebooking in this case, they can help you take a look at the price of the rebooking for your tickets. Our phone numbers can be located at https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards,
Anton.

@LJS2403 Hi! Please contact our phone support with your booking reference and we can help you take a look at the reservation to see what possibilities there are and what alternative connections are available. Phone numbers can be located at https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards,
Anton.

@TheSoccerDucks Hi! If you do not manage to keep your Diamond status, you might be allowed to receive an extension, you can find more info here: https://t.co/T05QTSSuuB
If you are not eligible for an extension you will go down to gold and loose your life time gold status. 
Kind regards, Rebecka

@JulieStampdk Okej jag förstår och vi beklagar igen att er resa ändrats. Om ni vill söka återbetalning för biljetterna så kan ni göra det hos resebyrån där ni bokat resan.

Med vänlig hälsning,
Anton.

@TheArtBureau Hi Jennifer
You are welcome to contact our customer service by phone or live chat https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj and we will try and help you further. 

Kind regards/Anna

@Nahren_Sy Hi Nahren 
We do not have any own requirements but follow the rules set by the country you are traveling to, you can find them via this link https://t.co/YhT9mVc7De 
Kind regards/ Anna

@brickeberg Hej Rossonero
Kontakta oss gärna på live chat , telefon https://t.co/z4gOZAAJQJ eller Facebook messenger så ska vi se vidare på detta med dig.

Hälsningar /Anna

@GelertNature Hello
Yes that is correct.

Kind regards /Anna

@dsfrederik Hi Frederik
Please contact us on live chat, phone https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj or Facebook messenger and we can help you further with this.

Kind regards /Anna

@rafaruizmalaga Hi, if this is a private travel (not SAS for Business contract) we are only able to send a receipt to you. If you selected invoice as payment method the invoice is not sent by us but from the bank/company that offered you the credit.

Best regards,
Anton.

@JulieStampdk Hej, vi beklagar att er resa ändrats och vi förstår att det orsakar svårigheter och obekvämligheter för er. Jag rekommenderar att ni ringer vår kundtjänst på tel +45 70 102 000 så kan de hjälpa er att kolla på andra alternativ att omboka till.

Med vänlig hälsning,
Anton.

@TemeSaarinen Hi! We are planning to fly to and from Åbo, Finland from March 2022 and onward.

Best regards,
Anton.

@mark_nuk Hi! 

SAS is for the time being limiting the number of allowed carry-on items to 1 per person. This means that you can no longer bring an additional personal item, such as a lap top or hand bag on top of your carry-on.

//Best regards, Dennis.

@sammaes Hi! This depends on what is included in the frequent traveler program that you are part of, for more information on what is included in Eurobonus Gold on Star Alliance flights you can visit  https://t.co/IIRy8cNe2w and click on "Benefits with Star Alliance"

Best regards,
Anton.

@Atreiu86 Hi, this error message most likely means that the ticket you are trying to book is displayed in another currency than the currency that the voucher is issued in. Please check so that the currencies match and try to book the ticket(s) again.

Best regards,
Anton.

@SimonHoejbjerg Hej! Vi beklagar att du upplever det så, om du önskar sända dina synpunkter till oss så rekomenderar jag att du använder vårt feedback-formulär https://t.co/wprQ9Zejqh

Med vänlig hälsning,
Anton.

@afternetman Hello, our phone lines are open between 07-19 CET timezone but the wait time may be longer than usual as many people are contacting us at the moment, today however the wait time is lower if you wish to try and call us again.

Best regards,
Anton.

@jockoconnell Hello, we are sorry to hear that your trip have received schedule changes. If you still need help with rebooking you can call us again today as the wait time is lower today.

Best regards,
Anton.

@brillemann Hello, we apologize for the inconvenience caused in this situation. If you wish to send us feedback regarding your experience please use our feedback form at https://t.co/wprQ9Zejqh

Best regards,
Anton.

@CheekyPhil15 Hi! In that case you most likely received a general information email as most destinations still require this. The latest entry information and requirements that we have received from IATA can be found at https://t.co/oj06rsDGPg

Best regards,
Anton.

@Phumu015 Hello! To request ticketing authority for SAS documents you have to contact BSP for approval. More information can be found at https://t.co/68MeBFNMKo

Best regards,
Anton.

@GameGabster Hi, it can take 2-3 weeks tp get the notification from Ebretro that they have register the points, depending on their current workload.

Regards,
Peter

@albert_wolszon Hi, if the travel restrictions change, and SAS still fly to the destination, you will receive a refund according to the ticket rules: https://t.co/SUGh1L1hGV
If you are unsure, we suggest to purchase a fully refundable ticket. 
Kind regards, Rebecka

@rafaruizmalaga Hello, if you have a SAS for business account please contact our Corporate Sales support for help with receiving your invoice. Phone numbers can be located at https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Best regards,
Anton.

@Harwhey Hej! 

Ja det verkar vara ett problem med det just nu, så du kan kontakta vår kundtjänst via chatt/Messenger eller telefon så kan vi hjälpa dig välja en sittplats. Du kan se vår kontakt info här: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

//Vänlig hälsning, Dennis.

@split211 Hello, you can find the prices for checked baggage on our website https://t.co/D2hgbao5NB

Best regards,
Anton.

@NalabalaSarah Hi, it is not possible to contact the refund department directly but please send us a message via Messenger or live-chat https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj and we can help you take a look at this.

Best regards,
Anton.

@jimrbob Hi! The live-chat is open 07-19 CET on regular work days, 09-17 CET on Saturdays and 09-18 CET on Sundays. You will be notified with a push notification in your browser when the expected wait time is less than 5 minutes.

Best regards,
Anton.

@ConsonniR Hi! I am sorry to hear about the delayed airplane and that you did not receive a goodiebag. I recommend that you open a claim about this with our Customer Care department https://t.co/wprQ9Zejqh

Best regards,
Anton.

@Noelle09003043 Hi, we can unfortunately not assist with tickets or bookings here on Twitter. Our phonesupport can help you look at the booking and issue the tickets if it is needed. https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Regards,
Peter

@NalabalaSarah Hi, It is unfortunately not possible for us at customer service to get a expected handling time on a specific voucher or case at our refund department. They send a email or SMS when the case is handled.

Regards,
Peter

@Yushanviolin Hi, We do not have our own requirements for tests or documentation for Covid. It is the countries' authorities that decide the entry restrictions and the latest information we have received is available on this page https://t.co/YhT9mUUweE

Regards,
Peter

@ullaskov Hej, Jag kan tyvärr inte se på bokningar eller ärenden som gäller betalning här på Twitter. Vänligen kontakta vår support på tel 21896400 så kan de se på vilken typ av biljett det är och vad den extra avgiften läggs till för. 

Hälsningar,
Peter

@rinajensen Hi Rina
We do not have a ny new information regarding that unfortunately , if it is updated it will show via this link https://t.co/VJ4UBuS10j
Kind regards /Anna

@viktorsafar Hi Viktor
It is to long of what has been decided as form of password.
Kind regards /Anna

@emlperry Hi Emma
You can contact SAS customer care that handles complaints and requests of compensation and they will look at this. We can not do anything from customer service so i advice you to make a case via https://t.co/cE0TvFYaMV you can choose general wievs.
Kind regards /Anna

@viktorsafar Hi Viktor
This policy is most likely set as security reasons so the password is not to short and easy to copy.
Kind regards /Anna

@Scarf_YT Hi Carles
I do not understand this, we usually do not ask our passengers to reconfirm their trips. Please contact us on live chat , phone https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj or Facebook messenger with your booking reference. 
Kind regards /Anna

@emlperry Hi Emma
Error ‘cannot use in this market’ means that you are trying to book and pay with another currency then the voucher has.  You can change country at the bottom on our start page.
Kind regards /Anna

@theShrillMarmot Hi Tom , Dick and Harry
We do not have any own requirements we follow the requirements set by the country you are traveling to and through.
Kind regards/Anna

@antonia_juel Hi Antonia
You are welcome to call us and we will help you with this https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj   klick on Customer service/Eurobonus and phone list will show.
Kind regards /Anna

@Pernille_ba Hej Pernille
Vi har inga egna krav om test utan följer de krav som landet satt, du kan finna dem via denna länk https://t.co/YhT9mVc7De eller så kan det finnas via https://t.co/yjo6HQTNmJ
Vänliga hälsningar/Anna

@jztlikehvn Hi
You can find the requirements via this link https://t.co/YhT9mVc7De or you can contact the embassy for information.
Kind regards /Anna

@Scarf_YT Hi Carles 
The best thing for you is to contact the selling agency, it is hard for us to confirm when the ticket is not ours. But we can take a look ,contact us on Facebook messenger or chat with booking reference https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj
Kind regards /Anna

@paul_winginit Hello! We are not able to assist with adding seating over Twitter unfortunately but I recommend that you contact us by phone for help with this. Phone numbers can be located at https://t.co/b3QIqPBI2R

Best regards,
Anton.

@djbradshaw1980 Hi, we are unfortunately not able to assist with individual cases here over Twitter. Please contact us by live-chat or phone for more assistance https://t.co/b3QIqPBI2R - We also recommend deleting this Tweet as it contains your booking references.

Best regards,
Anton.

@sarahspoon Hi! I'm not aware of any problems with the mobile version of our website at the moment but I recommend that you try clearing cache and cookies in your browser or try using another browser.

Best regards,
Anton.

@stfucad3 Hi! You are able to purchase an Adult or Youth ticket from the age of 12. The Youth ticket is available till the day before your 26th birthday. 
If the youth tickets are unavailable, you can purchase an Adult ticket instead.
Kind regards, Rebecka

@AVeryLoudNoise Hi! You can find the rules that SAS is following here: https://t.co/YhT9mUUweE
In general, it is the country that you are travelling to that decide what documentation that is required to fly, apart from the requirement to wear a facemask during our flights
Kind regards, Rebecka

@sam_fowler_97 Hi!

Unfortunately you can not combine two checked-in bags so I recommend you to take two bags with you.

Kind regards, Kevin

@rommelparas Hi!

I recommend you to take contact with us by by chat/phone and we will look in to you matter, you can find the local number by this link https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj.

kind regards, Kevin

@Gone_Fishing11 Hi!

I recommend you to take contact with us by phone/chat and we will look in to your matter, you can find the local number by this link https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj.

Kind regards, Kevin

@Tomisdebom Hi!

You can see the fees we have for checked baggage by this link https://t.co/D2hgbaFHcb.

Kind regards, Kevin

@triathlee Hi!
I recommend you to take contact with us over the phone and we will help you with booking the ticket that you are looking for, you can find the local number by this link https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Kind regards, Kevin
